The paper focuses on Real-Time Bidding (RTB) in display advertising, which involves data mining and bidding strategy development. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses statistical analysis and benchmark experiments, which could fall under the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also mentions bid optimization, which could be relevant to the Computational Economics and Finance (cs.CE) sub-category.
